te flower just beneath the water's surface, its beauty evident but achingly kept just out of reach. The film brought the flower into the sun so we could enjoy its texture and fragrance in more visceral fashion. Both are magnificent, just a different picture of the same flower.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIf you loved the film, you must read the book. It is a hauntingly beautiful novel different from anything else you'll ever read. Literary fiction can often be dry and unrewarding, a lot of beautiful words and lovely phrases meant to impress us, but all too often leaving us cold and disinterested. Such is not the case here. This is a perfect storm of prose and story achieved only once by Ondaatje. A masterwork of rich and evocative prose that will surely touch the heart, an organ of fire.","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/17994985?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1097074805"},"likeCount":131,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":28,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.XiF3Ami7bv16lTjBSz3GCA":{"id":"kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.XiF3Ami7bv16lTjBSz3GCA","__typename":"Contributor","works":{"__typename":"ContributorWorksConnection","totalCount":3}},"User:739464":{"id":739464,"__typename":"User","legacyId":739464,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1442509875i/739464._UY200_CR33,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":true,"textReviewsCount":256,"viewableName":"Colin Miller","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/739464-colin-miller","contributor":{"__ref":"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.XiF3Ami7bv16lTjBSz3GCA"},"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":20},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.dDaRDhpQL1nIt1Ded31t9A":{"id":"kca://review:goodr